Mark Watches *Band of Brothers*
----------------------------

Commissioned by his fans to watch a previously unknown to him historical mini-series, Mark Oshiro (of Mark Watches, Mark Reads, and Mark Does Stuff fame) takes on the 2001 Emmy Award-winning epic portraying Easy Company's experiences during WWII, completely unspoiled.

The videos contained herein are of Mark watching and reacting to the series, *not* the actual episodes of *Band of Brothers*.


